<Layout title="Why Your 500GB Drive Shows 465GB (Binary vs Decimal)" description="Understand why your hard drive or SSD shows less storage than advertised. The binary vs decimal measurement difference explained clearly with the math." keywords="binary vs decimal storage, hard drive shows less space, 500GB shows 465GB, storage capacity, GiB vs GB, binary storage, drive space missing">
